                          Iconian V1.90ß beta
                           February 26, 1994

This  document describes and explains Iconian V1.90 beta, an icon editor
that supports OS3.x functions.  It also supports AGA display modes, such
as palette sharing and 256 colors.

All  binaries,  executables,  source,  and  documentation  is  Copyright
